---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base title="Privacy Policy" description="Privacy policy for lastseason.co.uk" canonical="/privacy/">
  <div class="container">
    <section class="page-hero">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    </section>
    <section class="section prose">
      <p>Last updated: 20 July 2026</p>
      <p>lastseason.co.uk ("we", "us") respects your privacy. This policy explains what data we collect and how we use it.</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">Data we collect</h2>
      <p>If you allow analytics, Google Analytics 4 receives usage information such as pages visited, device category and approximate location. Analytics is not loaded before consent. We do not ask for an account or collect personal information unless you contact us directly.</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">Cookies</h2>
      <p>The site stores your analytics choice in local storage under <code>lastseason-analytics-choice</code>. If you use saved leagues or recently viewed pages, those preferences are also stored only in your browser under <code>lastseason-favourite-leagues</code> and <code>lastseason-history</code>. Google Analytics may set cookies only after you choose “Allow analytics”. No advertising platform is currently loaded.</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">Third-party links</h2>
      <p>Kit pages link to third-party retailers for convenience. A retailer link may be an affiliate link only when this is disclosed beside it; in that case we may receive a commission at no extra cost to you. Third-party sites have their own privacy policies.</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">Your rights</h2>
      <p>Under UK GDPR, you have the right to access, rectify, or delete any personal data we hold about you. Contact us at privacy@lastseason.co.uk for any data requests.</p>
    </section>
  </div>
</Base>
